The Oversight Committee shall be composed of the following members:
2 trustees from the grantee in interest, as defined in § 5-1202.2(a)(1) of the Natural Resources Article;
1 individual from the North Point Peninsula Community Coordinating Council;
1 individual from the Essex Middle River Civic Council, Inc.;
2 interested citizens, 1 of whom shall reside in the sixth legislative district, and 1 of whom shall reside in the seventh legislative district;
1 individual from the Baltimore County Waterman's Association;
1 individual who represents the pleasure boating industry in Baltimore County;
1 individual who represents the sport fishing or crabbing industry in Baltimore County;
1 individual from the Greater Dundalk Community Council; and
1 individual from the Hart and Miller Island Area Environmental Group, Inc.
